<h3 id="example-2--get-protected-properties">Example 2: Get Protected Properties</h3>

<p>This example shows you how to get the protected properties of a class.</p>

<pre><code class="language-php">
use GanbaroDigital\MissingBits\ClassesAndObjects\FilterClassProperties;

$props = FilterClassProperties::from(
    ExampleClass::class,
    ReflectionProperty::IS_PROTECTED
);
var_dump($props);
</code></pre>
<p>The code above produces this output on PHP v5.6.30, PHP v7.0.19, PHP v7.1.5:</p>

<pre>
array(2) {
  ["value2"]=>
  string(28) "I am protected static value2"
  ["trait2"]=>
  string(28) "I am protected static trait2"
}
</pre>